{"id":4051,"date":"2024-04-15T23:27:33","date_gmt":"2024-04-15T14:27:33","guid":{"rendered":"https://blogbooks.net/?p=4051"},"modified":"2024-04-15T23:27:36","modified_gmt":"2024-04-15T14:27:36","slug":"chromebook%e3%81%ae%e3%82%a2%e3%83%83%e3%83%97%e3%83%87%e3%83%bc%e3%83%88%e3%81%ae%e8%87%aa%e5%8b%95%e6%9b%b4%e6%96%b0%e3%81%ae%e6%ad%a2%e3%82%81%e6%96%b9%e6%94%b9","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https://blogbooks.net/chromebook/4051/","title":{"rendered":"Chromebookのアップデートの自動更新の止め方(改)"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>こんにちは。今回はChromebookのアップデートの自動更新の止め方の、簡単バージョンです。</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">協力者(discord)</h2>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>amakawa_</li>\n\n\n\n<li>shiokonbusan</li>\n\n\n\n<li>ryo_001339</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">使えるバージョン</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>作動確認されているバージョンは、114,116,118,119,120<br>おそらく115でも使えると思われます。<br>(僕がver.113で使えなかったため、113以下は使えないと思われます。)<br>※Policyなどでブロック？されている場合があります。</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">手順</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>ものすごく簡単です。<br>まずは設定を開き、「ネットワーク」という場所の、wifiの&#x25b6;の部分を押します。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img width=\"679\" height=\"125\" data-attachment-id=\"4052\" data-permalink=\"https://blogbooks.net/chromebook/4051/attachment/screenshot-2024-01-20-17-17-05/\" data-orig-file=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Screenshot-2024-01-20-17.17.05.png\" data-orig-size=\"679,125\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Screenshot-2024-01-20-17.17.05\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Screenshot-2024-01-20-17.17.05-300x55.png\" data-large-file=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Screenshot-2024-01-20-17.17.05.png\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Screenshot-2024-01-20-17.17.05.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4052\" srcset=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Screenshot-2024-01-20-17.17.05.png 679w, https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Screenshot-2024-01-20-17.17.05-300x55.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 679px) 100vw, 679px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>※ここからは、アップデートを止めたいwifiごとに何回かやる必要があります。<br>次にwifiの名前などが書かれている右側の&#x25b6;を押します。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img width=\"1024\" height=\"539\" data-attachment-id=\"4055\" data-permalink=\"https://blogbooks.net/chromebook/4051/attachment/screenshot-2024-01-20-16-49-35/\" data-orig-file=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Screenshot-2024-01-20-16.49.35.png\" data-orig-size=\"1362,717\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Screenshot-2024-01-20-16.49.35\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Screenshot-2024-01-20-16.49.35-300x158.png\" data-large-file=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Screenshot-2024-01-20-16.49.35-1024x539.png\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Screenshot-2024-01-20-16.49.35-1024x539.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4055\" srcset=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Screenshot-2024-01-20-16.49.35-1024x539.png 1024w, https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Screenshot-2024-01-20-16.49.35-300x158.png 300w, https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Screenshot-2024-01-20-16.49.35-768x404.png 768w, https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Screenshot-2024-01-20-16.49.35.png 1362w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>次に少しスクロールし、詳細設定という場所を押します。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img width=\"679\" height=\"79\" data-attachment-id=\"4056\" data-permalink=\"https://blogbooks.net/chromebook/4051/attachment/screenshot-2024-01-20-16-50-52/\" data-orig-file=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Screenshot-2024-01-20-16.50.52.png\" data-orig-size=\"679,79\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Screenshot-2024-01-20-16.50.52\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Screenshot-2024-01-20-16.50.52-300x35.png\" data-large-file=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Screenshot-2024-01-20-16.50.52.png\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Screenshot-2024-01-20-16.50.52.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4056\" srcset=\"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Screenshot-2024-01-20-16.50.52.png 679w, https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Screenshot-2024-01-20-16.50.52-300x35.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 679px) 100vw, 679px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>このようなものが出てくると思うので、上の画像のようにオンにします。<br>完了です。</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">終わり</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>個々でこれをやるのはめんどくさいかも知れませんが、ご了承ください。<br>閲覧頂きありがとうございました。</p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"こんにちは。今回はChromebookのアップデートの自動更新の止め方の、簡単バージョンです。","protected":false},"author":34,"featured_media":4216,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_jetpack_memberships_contains_paid_content":false,"footnotes":"","jetpack_publicize_message":"","jetpack_publicize_feature_enabled":true,"jetpack_social_post_already_shared":true,"jetpack_social_options":{"image_generator_settings":{"template":"highway","enabled":false}}},"categories":[2,6],"tags":[8,9,112,10,11,13,174,173,15],"jetpack_publicize_connections":[],"jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack_featured_media_url":"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/cHJpdmF0ZS9sci9pbWFnZXMvd2Vic2l0ZS8yMDIyLTA0L3Vwd2s2MTY4Mjc1Mi13aWtpbWVkaWEtaW1hZ2Uta293cjUydmUuanBn.webp","jetpack_shortlink":"https://wp.me/p5wAvD-13l","nishiki_blocks_pro":{"display_name":"takumi","author_link":"https://blogbooks.net/written-by/57bf3bb3101571e2e1d45e0b02d1a71e6736677c/","featured_image":"https://blogbooks.net/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/cHJpdmF0ZS9sci9pbWFnZXMvd2Vic2l0ZS8yMDIyLTA0L3Vwd2s2MTY4Mjc1Mi13aWtpbWVkaWEtaW1hZ2Uta293cjUydmUuanBn-640x360.webp","category":[{"name":"chromebook","link":"https://blogbooks.net/category/chromebook/","id":2},{"name":"ブロック回避","link":"https://blogbooks.net/category/chromebook/%e3%83%96%e3%83%ad%e3%83%83%e3%82%af%e5%9b%9e%e9%81%bf/","id":6}],"excerpt":"こんにちは。今回はChromebookのアップデートの自動更新の止め方の、簡単バージョンです。","terms":[{"term_id":2,"name":"chromebook","slug":"chromebook","term_group":0,"term_taxonomy_id":2,"taxonomy":"category","description":"","parent":0,"count":144,"filter":"raw"},{"term_id":6,"name":"ブロック回避","slug":"%e3%83%96%e3%83%ad%e3%83%83%e3%82%af%e5%9b%9e%e9%81%bf","term_group":0,"term_taxonomy_id":6,"taxonomy":"category","description":"","parent":2,"count":113,"filter":"raw"},{"term_id":8,"name":"chrome","slug":"chrome","term_group":0,"term_taxo